    "diffSummary": "Redesigned the desktop UI into a Zalo-style 3-pane layout with shadcn-svelte: a brand-blue icon RailNav, a ConversationList (search + rows with avatar/snippet/time/unread badge), a ChatPane (contact header, message bubbles, composer), and a ConnectBar for login/listen/open-thread. Added a reactive session store (src/lib/session.svelte.ts) that wraps the existing Tauri commands (cred_file_summary/login_from_file/start_listening_from_file/send_message) and derives conversation rows + per-thread message lists from the live zalo://message stream — no mock data. Added shadcn-svelte components (avatar/input/scroll-area/separator) and bits-ui; introduced a Zalo brand color in app.css. Frontend-only: the Rust core is unchanged. Verified with a real browser verify-ui golden-path run against the running app (page-load 200, screenshot captured, 0 console errors, 0 network failures).",
